            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EActs%207%3A1-29%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EActs%20of%20the%20Apostles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EStephen%20Addresses%20the%20Council%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20high%20priest%20asked%20Stephen%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAre%20these%20accusations%20true%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20was%20Stephen%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reply%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BBrothers%20and%20fathers%2C%20listen%20to%20me.%20Our%20glorious%20God%20appeared%20to%20our%20ancestor%20Abraham%20in%20Mesopotamia%20before%20he%20settled%20in%20Haran.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EMesopotamia%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20the%20region%20now%20called%20Iraq.%20%3Cem%3EHaran%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20city%20in%20what%20is%20now%20called%20Syria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EGod%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BLeave%20your%20native%20land%20and%20your%20relatives%2C%20and%20come%20into%20the%20land%20that%20I%20will%20show%20you.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Gen%2012%3A1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_4%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Abraham%20left%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Chaldeans%20and%20lived%20in%20Haran%20until%20his%20father%20died.%20Then%20God%20brought%20him%20here%20to%20the%20land%20where%20you%20now%20live.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_5%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20God%20gave%20him%20no%20inheritance%20here%2C%20not%20even%20one%20square%20foot%20of%20land.%20God%20did%20promise%2C%20however%2C%20that%20eventually%20the%20whole%20land%20would%20belong%20to%20Abraham%20and%20his%20descendants%26%23x2014%3Beven%20though%20he%20had%20no%20children%20yet.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_6%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EGod%20also%20told%20him%20that%20his%20descendants%20would%20live%20in%20a%20foreign%20land%2C%20where%20they%20would%20be%20oppressed%20as%20slaves%20for%20400%26%23xA0%3Byears.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_7%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BBut%20I%20will%20punish%20the%20nation%20that%20enslaves%20them%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20God%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3Band%20in%20the%20end%20they%20will%20come%20out%20and%20worship%20me%20here%20in%20this%20place.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A5-7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Gen%2012%3A7%3B%2015%3A13-14%3B%20Exod%203%3A12.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_7_8%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGod%20also%20gave%20Abraham%20the%20covenant%20of%20circumcision%20at